{
  "stem": "26609.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember that, when they came over to my place-- I was on the second floor, as I said, on [INAUDIBLE], in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And their officers knocked on-- as they knocked, we had to come straightaway.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I opened the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my husband was not at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But soon, I lost him, because the Russians took him away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They needed him much earlier then they took people into the war, men, especially, much, much early, because, as I mentioned, he an engineer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they needed him for machines, tanks, building machines, or something like it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember-- my daughter never remembers her father-- when they came over and took him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he didn't know where they would take him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He couldn't tell me anything, He just said, I will write-- I will write-- and left me penniless.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They-- the Russians, where he works with them for a short time before they took him, they said to my husband, they will look after me, and they will pay me monthly, or weekly, whatever.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They never did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They promised, but they never did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They didn't get-- I didn't get-- for his work, for months that they owed him, they didn't pay him everything at once.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly, monthly or weekly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They owed him quite a lot, and they didn't pay it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they took him away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "For a long time, I didn't hear from him anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And about a month later, or over a month later, I got the first letter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I recognized-- recognized his handwriting, but there was no address.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was a number, only.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
